  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">解題高手的錦囊妙計</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:20px;\">我記得宗翰老師在一個給高一新鮮人講座的課程裡，有一個系列課程叫做「解題高手的錦囊妙計」。這課程是所謂的「專家模式」。他展示了數學高手在高超解題手法背後的秘密。這些星從來不知道的觀念，讓他腦洞大開。後來宗翰老師將他的手寫筆記稿給了星一份。我收藏的這篇文，便是這系列課程的一部分。徵得老師的同意，和大家分享。</span><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/719551552330866/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/719551552330866/</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371358169-57841ae5.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371463307-981fb048.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371573149-5496a686.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371550963-40cbc31f.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371565168-a6491566.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371561580-7b0a1af2.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371582039-c75ae679.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371678189-523008f4.png\" /></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371652117-14fe2371.png\" /></div>\n\n<div class=\"column half pic-center-page\"><img src=\"pic/columns/2023073112371570615-439ceafb.png\"